## ðŸ“‘ Headers ç¤ºä¾‹

```python
RequestItem(
    url="https://httpbin.org/headers",
    method="GET",
    headers={
        "Accept-Encoding": "gzip, deflate, br",
        "Connection": "keep-alive",
        "X-Test-Header": "ChatGPT"
    },
    timeout=5.0
)
```

